Ohio Edison cites cost , debt cuts in net rise . Ohio Edison Corp said on that third quarter earnings increased slightly due to efforts to cut costs , improve operations and reduce debt . Ohio Edison posted third quarter earnings of $ 89 . 4 million or $ 0 . 62 a share on operating revenues of $ 646 . 9 million , compared to $ 87 . 7 million or $ 0 . 61 a share on operating revenues of $ 667 . 0 million a year ago . Third quarter retail sales dropped 1 . 6 percent , mainly due to lower air - conditioning loads , the company said . 
